    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/hierarchical-json-structure-construction/003",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "There are 6 tables: project, study, protocol, entity, measurement, and factor... A 'record' would be a named element inside a 'table', which would normally correspond to a row in a spreadsheet table. A 'field' would be a named element inside a 'record', which would normally correspond to a column in a spreadsheet table.",
