      "asbval:evidence_quote": "MESSES helps transform tabular data from multiple sources into a Metabolomics Workbench specific deposition format. The package provides three commands, extract, validate, and convert, that implement a natural data transformation workflow... The 'extract' command is used to transform tabular data into a representative JavaScript Object Notation (JSON) file format using a tagging system... The 'validate' command evaluates whether the extracted MESSES JSON representation conforms to a specific data schema... The 'convert' command is used to convert the MESSES JSON representation into the mwTab JSON and tab-delimited formats.",
      "asbval:note": "All core claims are directly supported: tagging system for extraction, JSONized intermediate format, schema validation, and conversion to mwTab formats.",
